  String badIdea = "127.0" + "0.1"; // this is not detected
}
     ]]></code>
    </test-code>

    <test-code>
        <description><![CDATA[
Null literal does not puke.
     ]]></description>
        <expected-problems>0</expected-problems>
        <code><![CDATA[
public class Foo {
  String bar = null;
}
     ]]></code>
    </test-code>

    <test-code>
        <description><![CDATA[
Non String literal does not puke.
     ]]></description>
        <expected-problems>0</expected-problems>
        <code><![CDATA[
